msgid ""
"Configure how bright “100%” on the normal brightness slider should be. Make "
"it as bright as you'd ever use it, as long as the HDR image still looks good "
"and the gradients are smooth."
msgstr ""
"Pielāgojiet, cik gaišs ir „100 %“ gaišums parastajos gaišuma iestatījumos. "
"Padariet to tik gaišu, cik vēlaties lietot, kamēr vien HDR attēli izskatās "
"labi un krāsu pārejas ir vienmērīgas."

